      <title>拜登政府提议禁止中国、俄罗斯汽车零部件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/biden-administration-proposes-ban-of-chinese-russian-car-parts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府提议制定一项规则，禁止销售和进口中国和俄罗斯制造的车联网硬件和软件，此举可能会增强美国抵御商务部所称“非常真实”的黑客威胁的安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/biden-administration-proposes-ban-of-chinese-russian-car-parts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 12:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
